To scale down the etcd cluster just perform a normal upgrade setting the *statefulset.replicaCount* value to the desired number of nodes. For example, reduce the cluster to the default one replica:

~~~
$ helm upgrade bitnami/etcd \
--set statefulset.replicaCount=1
~~~
